{"tid":909994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國法官一夫當關  擋川普移民庇護禁令","createTime":"2018-11-20T22:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T01:35:44.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bb4b48f6367a93611a7a792be27128c72260d622","tid":909994,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T22:44:25.000Z","msg":"美國法官一夫當關 擋川普移民庇護禁令<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201811200325.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201811200325.aspx&d=lYAFvjf5Szr3PiovwE4oN8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f7dc0d15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201811200325.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社舊金山20日綜合外電報導）美國聯邦法官提格暫時阻擋美國總統川普頒布的一項禁令，這項命令禁止從墨西哥非法入境的移民申請庇護，這是川普移民政策在法庭上遭逢的最新挫敗。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦地區法官提格（Jon Tigar）在舊金山頒布對抗川普移民庇護禁令的臨時禁制令，立即生效且適用於全國，且將持續至12月19日，屆時提格預定展開聽審，考量更長期的禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n川普針對大規模移民潮，頒布這項移民公告，規定美國移民官員只能接受透過合法管道入境的移民申請庇護。民權團體指控川普11月9日頒布的命令，違反行政與移民法規。<br />\n<br />\n提格說明他的裁決指出，國會明確授權，移民可申請庇護，不論他們如何入境美國。提格指稱，川普頒布的最新規範嚴重背離先前慣例。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">提格說：「不論總統的權限有多大，他不能改寫移民法規，實施國會已明確禁止的條件。」</span><br />\n<br />\n提格是由前總統歐巴馬任命。先前川普的多項移民政策，包括針對庇護城市祭出的措施，也曾被聯邦法院阻擋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vcwVf4i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvcwVf4i.png&h=29eed3c0&s={SIZE}\" />（譯者：曹宇帆/核稿：劉學源）"},{"pid":"054ec39ccd14abacbda16ac4470bf18353d49980","tid":909994,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T22:46:48.000Z","msg":"抵壘政策<br />\n去轉中美洲做美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868a770602ef522632cb77ccbfee377db8788cb5","tid":909994,"uid":26329,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:15:03.000Z","msg":"移咩民ii就ii啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22332033265429a913213741559e9184940719c","tid":909994,"uid":64191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:24:26.000Z","msg":"哥德人大舉進攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac2b16e18daa5bf8a7e1f483682cddaf9f5e2c8","tid":909994,"uid":39383,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:29:15.000Z","msg":"講到個法官好正義咁"},{"pid":"9108d65d2cc99127d44d76ebf021f0fd1ee11a7d","tid":909994,"uid":37069,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:33:43.000Z","msg":"比晒佢哋去加州啦"},{"pid":"f97c31e091f9dbf8f9ea08f10b4783f3ac16170c","tid":909994,"uid":163826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:47:13.000Z","msg":"個官住係邊？送晒去佢附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064442a30a42b065457044d7565a9cc7dff2977b","tid":909994,"uid":77092,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:49:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d1f0df8176772da5991e5bfc986c88bd676ed18","tid":909994,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:50:30.000Z","msg":"中國人飛去墨西哥再上路得唔得"},{"pid":"34e644b3973356eab5596f544f90ea5088abbeea","tid":909994,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T00:09:27.000Z","msg":"On9  加州收？"},{"pid":"a0df6b9f4588db7412e3fe7c1a9c00b5be3599f9","tid":909994,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T00:55:18.000Z","msg":"班垃圾冇錢就借左膠大愛嘅口號去黐飲黐食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e8f10366db6323c60b7111fc3adea17fa2f6c1","tid":909994,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime